deepl:Debug logging to file and syslog.original: Debug logging to file and syslog
deepl:Debug logging to file and syslog.translation: Logging di debug su file e syslog

deepl:New ports get instantly opened on.original: New ports get instantly opened on daemon start
deepl:New ports get instantly opened on.translation: Le nuove porte vengono aperte istantaneamente all'avvio del daemon

deepl:On configuration changes old ports.original: On configuration changes old ports are updated after the first intervall
deepl:On configuration changes old ports.translation: In caso di modifica della configurazione, le vecchie porte vengono aggiornate dopo il primo intervento

deepl:Open ports could not be closed and.original: Open ports could not be closed and you have wait for the timeout
deepl:Open ports could not be closed and.translation: Non è possibile chiudere le porte aperte e bisogna attendere il timeout

deepl:Ports to open, multiple seperated.original: Ports to open, multiple seperated by spaces
deepl:Ports to open, multiple seperated.translation: Porte da aprire; più valori vanno separati da spazi

deepl:The ports will be opened for maxim.original: The ports will be opened for maximum 120 seconds and need to be refreshed afterwards
deepl:The ports will be opened for maxim.translation: Le porte saranno aperte per un massimo di 120 secondi e dovranno poi essere aggiornate
